00:22:05.890 --> 00:22:07.850
¡Vaya!

334
00:22:08.880 --> 00:22:10.830
Gracias.

335
00:22:18.490 --> 00:22:23.470
¡Beso, beso, beso!

336
00:22:23.470 --> 00:22:26.090
- Detente. 
